HEADWORD: Onoclea
<hw>Onoclea</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>A genus consisting of only
species: the sensitive fern; in some classifications it is included in
the <fam>Polypodiaceae</fam>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> genus <gen>Onoclea</gen>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

